# Maintained Documents

> A registry of all documents that must be kept up to date as the project evolves.

---

## Purpose

This file tracks which documents exist, who is responsible for maintaining them, and when they should be updated. During Auto-Flow STEP 4 (Self-Review), the Developer AI checks if any maintained documents need updating based on the changes made.

